name: The Dirty Hands of the Machine - 2
description: This is piece number 2 of the 3-part series "The Dirty Hands of the Machine" - the first ever attempt of creating graffiti pieces on passenger trains using artificial intelligence (i.e. machine learning). This image was created by training a StyleGan 1 model on ~6000 image frames from the classic European graffiti movie “Dirty Handz 3” (Roma Bonus Footage 95/96). The piece was created in 2019. 1800x1800px, PNG / Created by Alsino Skowronnek / Instagram: @alsinoskowronnek
